<L>__{interior lancey's hotel room}
<A>__{lancey has decided on a change of costume from his last game, and this time he goes for the old fashioned velvet smoking jacket and silk foulard. over this he puts on a light overcoat. then he assembles medicines, toilet articles and money, putting them all into a small satchel. finally, he puts on his hat and goes to the door.}
<L>__{interior plush hotel corridor}
<A>__{we follow lancey's progress as far as the elevator.}
